videos.description: Joe Ingles tosses the ball over to Jordan Clarkson, who smoothly drains a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ingles feeds Clarkson for a 3-pointer) 2021/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ingles feeds Clarkson for a 3-pointer

videos.description: Shake Milton lobs it up to Dwight Howard, who finishes with a two-handed flush.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Milton lofts it up to Howard for a jam) 2021/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Milton lofts it up to Howard for a jam

videos.description: Ben Simmons drives past half court and toward the bucket for a one-handed dunk plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Simmons speeds in for the and-1 dunk) 2021/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons speeds in for the and-1 dunk

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell nearly throws down a massive dunk over Joel Embiid, but he still gets the bucket to fall while drawing a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mitchell nearly posterizes Embiid, still gets and-1) 2021/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mitchell nearly posterizes Embiid, still gets and-1

videos.description: Joel Embiid rushes behind the 3-point line and knocks down the shot to tie the game at 118-118 as the Jazz and the 76ers head to overtime.
videos.headline: Embiid drains game-tying 3-pointer

videos.description: Joel Embiid successfully pleads with the referees to give Donovan Mitchell a technical foul for arguing. Shortly after that, Mitchell gets his second tech and is ejected.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid lobbies for Mitchell to get tech) 2021/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid lobbies for Mitchell to get tech

videos.description: Tobias Harris scores 11 of the 76ers' 13 points in overtime as Philadelphia holds off Utah 131-123.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Harris drops 11 points in OT to lead Sixers to win) 2021/03/03 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Harris drops 11 points in OT to lead Sixers to win

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell doesn't hold back as he shares his displeasure with the referees in the Jazz's overtime loss to the 76ers.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Mitchell blasts refs after loss to Sixers: 'We won this game') 2021/3/3

videos.headline: Mitchell blasts refs after loss to Sixers: 'We won this game'
